{"tid":2392026,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"李宗德小學早會展示Momo恐怖圖 警惕學生不要接觸 反嚇壞小朋友","createTime":"2021-02-02T14:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T00:31:02.000Z","uid":137725,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a2a487927f801f7672d3e60cb173bc670f118b","tid":2392026,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"2019年3月8日 19:02<br />\n近日，鼓吹兒童自殺遊戲「Momo challenge」在網上流傳，不少小朋友被「嚇親」。故此，日前有小學教師，希望在早會上教育學生不要接觸momo的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n李宗德小學早會展示Momo恐怖圖<br />\n<br />\n上周五，天水圍的和富慈善基金李宗德小學有老師在早會上，教育學生不要亂上YouTube，接觸momo的遊戲。然而，在投影機屏幕上展示Momo恐怖圖，圖片「一閃即刻消失」，但嚇得在場600多名學生尖聲大叫。其後，有學生在WhatsApp群組開始瘋傳Momo圖片，令更多學生受驚，甚至有學生要移除YouTube應用程式、有學生出現失眠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恐怖網絡自殺遊戲「MOMO」<br />\n<br />\n「MOMO」，目的是引誘青少年自殘和自殺，利用Whatsapp傳播信息，隨機聯絡別人，以騷擾挑釁等方式，誘使對方參與各類挑戰，做出各種自殘、危險的行為，甚至包括自殺。阿根廷一名12歲少女就被懷疑因參與遊戲而上吊自殺。近日，Momo challenge又捲土重來，滲入YouTube中，在正常卡通播到一半然後MOMO出現包括peppa pig，令家長防不勝防。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張嘉兒都在Facebook呼籲家長要小心，「超恐怖，超不安，但係都照post因為真係要注意一。我不嬲都唔會比我個女睇YouTube睇電視嘅，但係大家小心比佢哋睇嗰陣時有呢個咁嘅恐怖人物出現啊。個恐怖人物(一個自殺遊戲嘅廣告）會話我要殺咗你同埋唆擺小朋友去殺人。大家睇YouTube嗰時小心呢個遊戲嘅廣告佢彈出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n12歲女童因玩Momo上吊自殺<br />\n<br />\n上年9月，警方先發現一具16歲少年屍體，2日後一名12歲女童上吊自殺，兩名死者都被發現電話內有「Momo」自殺遊戲的訊息，當地媒體推斷2人認識，認為少年在自殺前把遊戲傳給對方，挑戰對方了結生命。近日，英國也有5歲女童突然亂剪自己頭髮，呼籲家長要多加注意。<br />\n<br />\n對此，YouTube 官方回應，「我們沒有證據顯示有任何影片展示或推廣Momo挑戰的視頻。此類內容將違反我們的政策，並在舉報時立即刪除。」（Contrary to press reports, we have not received any evidence of videos showing or promoting the Momo challenge on YouTube. Content of this kind would be in violation of our policies and removed immediately when flagged.）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係時候bin c班教畜"},{"pid":"9074b8226d8207b0a1f25a6039979d760c56c900","tid":2392026,"uid":137725,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">自己on99，累班小朋友有陰影，有冇清 update吓個畜牲近況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"3fd43e9c142fb3debb1b009e722fc12fb8cb73e2","tid":2392026,"uid":294343,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:28:56.000Z","msg":"咁下次叫人叫班學生唔好睇咸片係咪開pornhub"},{"pid":"29e87f9af6b66d2f4456d007e2b2e52cffe269cc","tid":2392026,"uid":57287,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:43:05.000Z","msg":"old news <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abe6759f4d880a53b55ed14e440f78438411906","tid":2392026,"uid":267632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"呢個post一定會有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47a0e2a9332eec25326f6b8500414c3f07d75e3","tid":2392026,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:23:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.abc.net.au/cm/rimage/10861096-16x9-xlarge.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fcm%2Frimage%2F10861096-16x9-xlarge.jpg&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPreIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=70745b1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.abc.net.au/cm/rimage/10861096-16x9-xlarge.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"366da9d66c0ae6e363bcc0ef537e0ff97dd62f84","tid":2392026,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f291747567c7b3a8f06daf8bcc6ce7a20083945","tid":2392026,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T23:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cf4f67c63c14897827d7007b1fc234eb